[[黃草體|黃草體]]是由[[美籍華裔|美籍華裔]]書法家[[黃彰任|黃彰任]]所創的漢字[[草書|草書]]字體。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://vic.sina.com.cn/news/27/2009/0818/4524.html |title=黄草字体 |accessdate=2011-07-03 |archive-date=2013-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130220235112/http://vic.sina.com.cn/news/27/2009/0818/4524.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>其特點在於改變了昔日草書體難於識別的問題，具有規範化、標準化的書寫特徵，並形成了完整的字庫體系。<ref name="黄彰任">{{cite book | language = zh-hans | author = 黄彰任 | coauthors = | title = 常用黄草字库 | url = | date = 1997年 | location = | publisher = 浙江大学出版社 | isbn = 7-308-01924-1| ref =}}</ref>在保留草書原有寫法的前提下，單字獨立成章，並對筆畫適當縮減，融[[簡體|簡體]]、[[繁體|繁體]]寫法於一體，易寫易識。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.foundertype.com/showsortpic.php?inputword=%E6%96%B9%E6%AD%A3%E9%BB%84%E8%8D%89&sid=279&fontfile=FZHCJW.TTF |title=方正黄草 - 设计理念 |accessdate=2020-09-23 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306022009/http://www.foundertype.com/showsortpic.php?inputword=%E6%96%B9%E6%AD%A3%E9%BB%84%E8%8D%89&sid=279&fontfile=FZHCJW.TTF |dead-url=no }}</ref>

經[[北京|北京]][[方正集團|方正集團]]於1999年開發的黃草體計算機字庫<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.foundertype.com/index/manual/101/fzfont2010.html |title=方正字库2010产品手册 168頁 |accessdate=2011-07-03 |archive-date=2011-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110707060347/http://www.foundertype.com/index/manual/101/fzfont2010.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，現已廣泛用於標題、廣告、書法摹寫等領域。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.foundertype.com/showsortpic.php?inputword=%E6%96%B9%E6%AD%A3%E9%BB%84%E8%8D%89&sid=279&fontfile=FZHCJW.TTF |title=方正黄草 - 应用方案 |accessdate=2020-09-23 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306022009/http://www.foundertype.com/showsortpic.php?inputword=%E6%96%B9%E6%AD%A3%E9%BB%84%E8%8D%89&sid=279&fontfile=FZHCJW.TTF |dead-url=no }}</ref>

